data.text:
The GOP Doctors Caucus (@GOPDoctors) is composed of medical providers who utilize their healthcare expertise and backgrounds to develop patient-centered health care policy. I served as co-chair, along with Congressmen Brad Wenstrup, D.P.M. (OH-02) and Michael Burgess, M.D. (TX-26) from 2018-2022.

Currently, the GOP Doctors Caucus is Co-Chaired by Congressmen Brad Wenstrup, D.P.M. (OH-02), Michael Burgess, M.D. (TX-26), and Greg Murphy, M.D. (NC-03).
